1 (4) Three members of the Senate, one of whom must be a member of the minority
2 party, appointed by the executive board.
3 If the chair of a committee is unable to serve on the task force, the Executive Board
4 of the Legislative Research Council may appoint another member of the committee to
5 serve in the chair's place.
